1
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,879
Here in Zhenyuan County,

2
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,400
you dare lay hands on the Imperial Uncle?

3
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,480
Ning Chen.

4
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,599
The Imperial Uncle defied Da Xuan's laws,

5
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,280
preyed upon the common people,

6
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,799
and his crimes warrant death.

7
00:01:41,879 --> 00:01:43,239
Come with me to the capital for trial.

8
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,599
Insolence!

9
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:45,640
How dare you!

10
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,120
This is the Imperial Uncle!

11
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,480
Imperial Inspectorate business!

12
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,760
All bystanders, get out of the way!

13
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,079
Anyone who disobeys

14
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,280
dies.

15
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,599
Arrogant fool!

16
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,560
Golden Guard Pan,

17
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:01,879
does your Inspectorate have any rules left?

18
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,359
Calm your anger, Imperial Uncle.

19
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:05,959
Ning Chen,

20
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,840
the Imperial Uncle is royal kin.

21
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:08,599
Even if he is guilty,

22
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,159
His Majesty must decide his fate.

23
00:02:10,719 --> 00:02:11,520
Lower your blade.

24
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,319
Even the emperor is equal under the law.

25
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,879
The blade in my hand

26
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,479
answers only to the law,

27
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:20,479
not to royal kin.

28
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,280
You—

29
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,800
Golden Guard Pan,

30
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,319
you've seen it all, haven't you?

31
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,960
The people around here are in rags,

32
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:27,879
unable to fill their bellies,

33
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,800
even the tree bark has been stripped clean.

34
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,240
And what are you doing?

35
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,520
Feasting on meat, women, and fine wine.

36
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,840
Don't you feel the slightest unease or guilt?

37
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,159
Since when do you get to lecture me?

38
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,240
The law demands it.

39
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,759
Everyone present here today,

40
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,479
every single one of you,

41
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,479
will return to the capital for trial.

42
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,400
You included.

43
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,400
What a mighty official you are!

44
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,439
Golden Guard Pan,

45
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:03,120
this man has run wild in my estate

46
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,879
and tried to harm royal kin.

47
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,639
His crime warrants beheading.

48
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:09,960
Ning Chen,

49
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,840
I'll say it one last time:

50
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,639
lower your blade.

51
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,319
Before you give me orders,

52
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,759
shouldn't you reflect on your own deeds?

53
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:21,240
Are you worthy of the uniform you wear?

54
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,759
This uniform of mine

55
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,719
wasn't earned by coasting on seniority.

56
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,960
Fine.

57
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,719
Then let's see

58
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:36,039
whether you can protect him today.

59
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,400
You brought this on yourself.

60
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:43,280
Golden Guard Pan, impressive skills indeed.

61
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,960
Is this how you wield your blade?

62
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,639
Imperial Uncle, are you all right?

63
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,199
Get lost!

64
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,120
Guards!

65
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,719
Drag this traitor away

66
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,599
and publicly chop him up for the dogs!

67
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,520
Let's see who'll dare,

68
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,240
ever again in Zhenyuan County,

69
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:05,400
to cross the Imperial Uncle.

70
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,199
Hold on.

71
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:08,319
Calm your anger, Imperial Uncle.

72
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,759
Ning Chen is His Majesty's Silver Guard.

73
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,719
Even if he's guilty,

74
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,319
His Majesty must judge him.

75
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,120
Rest assured, Imperial Uncle.

76
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,720
What has happened today

77
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,399
will never leak out.

78
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,480
Remember what you just said.

79
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,360
Let go of me!

80
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,480
Let go of me!

81
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,240
Let go!

82
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:40,399
The day is still young.

83
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,759
I'll treat you to quite a show.

84
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,439
Lian'er!

85
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,279
Ning Chen!

86
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,040
Since you know

87
00:04:58,279 --> 00:05:00,879
that Zhenyuan County is my turf,

88
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:04,040
how dare you leave them right there?

89
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,000
Do you know how many spies

90
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:08,040
I have in Zhenyuan County?

91
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,920
The moment you walked away,

92
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:12,959
my men dragged them right back.

93
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:16,600
You say I abduct innocent women,

94
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:18,240
that I treat lives like dirt.

95
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,759
Well, let me tell you,

96
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,480
you're absolutely right.

97
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,519
And what are you going to do about it?

98
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:25,839
Ning Chen!

99
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:26,600
Ning Chen!

100
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,800
You beast!

101
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,720
Ning Chen!

102
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:38,720
Boy,

103
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:41,000
can't take it anymore?

104
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,519
Today the Imperial Uncle will teach you

105
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:46,240
what royalty really means.

106
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,759
This whole realm belongs to my family.

107
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,399
I am the law! I am heaven itself!

108
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:53,160
You beast!

109
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:55,160
Lian'er!

110
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,959
Let go!

111
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,199
You beast!

112
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,160
Let me go!

113
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,879
Ning Chen! Ning Chen!

114
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,240
Imperial Uncle!

115
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:34,959
Father!

116
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,199
I... I...

117
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:47,959
What is going on here?

118
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,600
Chief!

119
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,879
He deserved it!

120
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,399
A righteous kill!

121
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:52,720
This is a disaster!

122
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,399
Take Ning Chen away.

123
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,199
I'll walk on my own.

124
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,199
You!

125
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,920
Guard him well.

126
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,079
He deserved it!

127
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,079
A righteous kill!

128
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,079
Our righteous lord!

129
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,759
I'm a Silver Guard of the Imperial Inspectorate.

130
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,600
I take the sovereign's pay,

131
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,720
and bear the sovereign's burdens.

132
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,639
I'm not worth kneeling for.

133
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,199
All of you, rise.

134
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,279
No, look at you.

135
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,839
At least eat a few bites.

136
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,879
It's been days. Come on.

137
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,839
If you keep this up,

138
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,240
before we even get back to the capital,

139
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,199
your body will give out first.

140
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:18,319
Golden Guard Pan sent word to the capital.

141
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,959
Brothers from other prefectures

142
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,680
will come to handle the aftermath.

143
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,759
Don't mention him to me.

144
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,480
Ning.

145
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,319
You've truly misunderstood the chief.

146
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,000
Misunderstood?

147
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,840
He took bribes from the Imperial Uncle.

148
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:36,480
How did I misunderstand him?

149
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,960
The chief did that

150
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,960
to placate the officials of Zhenyuan County.

151
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:46,200
The dirty silver has all been catalogued

152
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,279
and sent to the capital.

153
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,399
That dirty silver

154
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,240
will be the evidence to convict them later.

155
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:57,840
Then why stop me from arresting him?

156
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,039
Why?

157
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:00,919
Be...

158
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,759
Because you were too impulsive.

159
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,159
Ning Chen.

160
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,679
The Imperial Inspectorate came here

161
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,919
to purge all of Chongzhou's officialdom.

162
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,600
How could you arrest him without evidence?

163
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:13,720
Fine.

164
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:15,039
Even if you used force,

165
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,320
and dragged him back to the capital,

166
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,840
and accused him of reckless murder,

167
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,759
of abducting common women,

168
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,720
where's the evidence?

169
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,840
How could you convict him without proof?

170
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:27,480
What's more,

171
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:29,399
the chief stopped you to protect you.

172
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,600
That single strike of yours,

173
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,200
sure, you vented your anger,

174
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,879
but didn't you throw your own life away?

175
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,679
You fool!

176
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,120
When the emperor rages,

177
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,000
millions of corpses fall.

178
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,840
A commoner's rage spills blood three feet.

179
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,039
Even with only a commoner's courage,

180
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,759
I have no regrets.

181
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,919
If I had to do it again,

182
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,440
I'd still slaughter that beast.

183
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,000
Wasted my breath.

184
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:07,840
By the way,

185
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,440
how are Old Li and A-Lian?

186
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,919
Golden Guard Pan sent them home.

187
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,080
You should worry about yourself instead.

188
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,600
Well, he did one decent thing.

189
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,360
Ning.

190
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,960
Be honest with me.

191
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:26,200
Is it that you don't trust the chief?

192
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:30,480
And don't trust us two brothers either?

193
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,360
That Pan, I definitely don't trust.

194
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,519
As for you two,

195
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,679
you'd better not get tangled up with me,

196
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,159
to avoid being dragged down.

197
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,320
It really was our fault.

198
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,559
We didn't watch over you.

199
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,600
If you'd stayed with us the whole time,

200
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,159
none of this would have happened.

201
00:11:02,399 --> 00:11:03,600
We shouldn't have brought you to Zhenyuan County.

202
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:10,639
By the mandate of Heaven,

203
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,399
Silver Guard Ning Chen of the Imperial Inspectorate,

204
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:16,600
defied the law in gross insubordination,

205
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,440
slaying the Imperial Uncle by the blade.

206
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:20,360
For such reckless audacity,

207
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:23,519
he is stripped of his Silver Guard rank,

208
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,399
escorted back to the capital,

209
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:27,600
strictly tried and sentenced,

210
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:30,200
and executed according to the law.

211
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,639
Lord Ning! Lord Ning! Lord Ning!

212
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,240
Stop the cart!

213
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:34,120
Lord Ning!

214
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,519
Lord Ning has been wronged!

215
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,159
Yes!

216
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:41,120
We beg you officials to see the truth!

217
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:42,960
Lord Ning doesn't deserve to die!

218
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:45,000
He's a good man!

219
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:46,679
Please spare Lord Ning!

220
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,200
Lord Ning has been wronged!

221
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,919
The Imperial Uncle was pure evil!

222
00:11:59,120 --> 00:11:59,559
That's right!

223
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:01,799
Get up.

224
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,759
All of you, please get up.

225
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,399
We beg you, my lord!

226
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,759
We beg you, my lord!

227
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:12,399
Please spare Lord Ning, my lord!

228
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,840
Please spare Lord Ning!

229
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,519
My lord!

230
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,639
My lord!

231
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:19,039
We just want to see Lord Ning off.

232
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,159
Please show some leniency, my lord.

233
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,240
Yes, please!

234
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,159
Lord Ning.

235
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:33,200
On behalf of the people of Zhenyuan County,

236
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:35,159
this old man thanks you.

237
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,559
Lord Ning.

238
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:43,679
Thank you, Lord Ning.

239
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,679
Thank you, Lord Ning.

240
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:50,879
My lord.

241
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,399
Take these to eat on the road.

242
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,200
My lord, Lord Ning.

243
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,919
We don't have much at home.

244
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,360
Please take this, my lord.

245
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,320
My lord, please take it.

246
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:10,799
Big brother.

247
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:12,720
Mama said you're a good man.

248
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,360
You must take this.

249
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,759
Lord Ning.

250
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:19,039
Take this water to drink on the road.

251
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:28,679
It's just a small token.

252
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:29,639
Lord Ning.

253
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,399
Please take this.

254
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:34,919
Have a bit to eat on the way.

255
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,600
My lord! My lord!

256
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,919
Take care, my lord.

257
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,679
Take care!

258
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,120
Overseeing the officials,

259
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,360
rooting out the corrupt,

260
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,279
this is simply what we ought to do.

261
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,759
I am a prisoner of the imperial court.

262
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,639
I must return to the capital for trial.

263
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,799
They wouldn't dare do anything to me.

264
00:14:04,519 --> 00:14:05,399
Hurry on home now.

265
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,320
You must take care, my lord!

266
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,159
All of you, head home.

267
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:12,759
My lord! My lord!

268
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:14,279
Take care, my lord!

269
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,080
Take care, my lord!

270
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,240
Take care, Lord Ning!

271
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:25,080
Take care, my lord!

272
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,519
Let's go.

273
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,600
Move out!

274
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:36,240
Lord Ning, my lord, take care!

275
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,879
Thank you, Lord Ning!

276
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:41,519
My lord, take care!

277
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,039
Lord Ning!

278
00:14:45,159 --> 00:14:46,799
Lord Ning, you must take care!

279
00:14:46,919 --> 00:14:49,679
Hewn from deep mountains by countless blows,

280
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:54,720
it endures the raging flames with ease.

281
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,840
Though shattered to dust, it stands unafraid,

282
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:05,519
to leave its purity in this world.

283
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,919
If justice is absent from this world,

284
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:15,840
I will wield my blade to slay the wolves.

285
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,840
